<D>__{wait.}
<A>__{she takes the carnation out of her lapel, starts to put it in bud's buttonhole.}
<C>__{bud}
<D>__{thank you. that's the first thing i ever noticed about you when you were still on the local elevator you always wore a flower }
<A>__{the elevator buzzer is now sounding insistently. fran steps back inside.}
